If anyone finds this thread later, the script mentioned in the doc above worked. Basically you prevent loading any scripts that are only best used when viewing the live page and not editing. In my case it was a hash scroll function.

```jQuery(document).ready(function($) {
  if (window.hsInEditor) {
    return;
  }
  // other stuff
  $('.some_widget').fancyThing();
});```
